      ** ======

      ** Error fields/message IDs/message data (arrays) from/to caller
     C                   PARM                    FldNamXAr
     C                   PARM                    MsgIdXAr
     C                   PARM                    MsgDtaXAr

      ** Internal funding deals error indicator file
     C                   PARM                    OkFlags

      ** New Deal in File Format of main deal
     C                   PARM                    NwDlFilFmt1

      ** Redisplay screen flag
     C                   PARM                    PReDsp

